Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_CODACS(zc) From W1SMH1
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_CODACS(zc) From W1SMH1
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_CODACS(zc) From W1SMH1
