Subprog AS_CODACT(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
Local Integer INDIC : INDIC = indice
Raz mkstat
Call TEXTE(186,GBOUT1) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(6028,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_CODACT(zc) From W1SMH1
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_CODACT(zc) From W1SMH1
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_CODACT(zc) From W1SMH1
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_CODACT(zc) From W1SMH1
