$ON_OPT
Onevent BEFORE_INPUT Call AS_OPT(zc) From W1SMH1
Onevent INIT_AREA Call D_OPT(zc) From W1SMH1
Onevent CONTROL Call C_OPT(zc) From W1SMH1
